<http://drug.uk/usage/hepatic-impairment/a7d2d220-b641-4291-b910-e23d5764fb09> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> " Manufacturer advises caution in mild to moderate impairment (or if hepatic transaminases greater than 2 times the upper limit of normal, or if bilirubin is equal or greater than 1.5 times the upper limit of normal); avoid in severe impairment or impairment associated with coagulopathy and clinically relevant bleeding risk." .
